FBIS3-32647 "drlat030bb_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 INTER-AMERICAN AFFAIRS Mercosur Foreign Ministers To Meet in Buenos Aires March PY1102192994 Buenos Aires Radio Nacional Network in Spanish 1600 GMT 11 Feb 94 PY1102192994 Buenos Aires Radio Nacional Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The foreign ministers of the Mercosur [Common Market of the South] countries will meet in Buenos Aires on 9 March. Uruguayan Foreign Minister Sergio Abreu reported that the foreign ministers of the Mercosur countries will review a Brazilian proposal to form a regional free trade zone and establish a common external tariff. The meeting date was decided during an informal meeting held by the foreign ministers of Argentina, Brazil, Uruguay, and Paraguay.
